<section id="prompt-engineering-a-systematic-study" class="level1">
<h1>Prompt Engineering: A Systematic Study</h1>
<p>This experiment explores how different prompt engineering techniques affect the quality and consistency of AI-generated content. I’ll be testing various approaches using GPT-4 as the base model.</p>
<section id="experiment-objective" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="experiment-objective">Experiment Objective</h2>
<p>To quantitatively and qualitatively assess how different prompt structures influence: 1. Output consistency 2. Content relevance 3. Response specificity 4. Creative variation</p>
</section>
<section id="methodology" class="level2">
